songs.title: Astral Bacchanalia
songs.lyrics:
Upper dimensions where the spirits drone
Ancestral knowledge that no man has known
A masterful secret the terror withholds
Astral bacchanalia the flames of the sun
When theres no end, no beginning
Lunatic exposure the universe dwell
Demential majesty planets collide
Empty solutions the oceans in black
Show me the answer
Bring me the answer
Drunken abraxas
The call of the sun
Birds on fire eternal pyre
Traveling elsewhere spreading the word
Breaking the sorrow next blasting hollow
The last attraction elixirs of good
Wild and the mystics the goddess conspiracy
Cursed by the amazing empires of dust
Empty solutions the oceans in black
Cult of the winter the darkest demise
Show me the answer
Bring me the answer
Drunken abraxas
The call of the sun
